      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle stands as a definitive testament to meticulous preservation and uncompromising maintenance. The exterior retains its original factory luster, complemented by an interior that remains in pristine, untouched state. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously vetted to ensure it meets our most exacting standards for excellence. This offering represents an unparalleled acquisition opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands the pinnacle of automotive quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
